data.description: Built in 2021, this fine 3BR/2BA home "stands out" to most new construction in the area, not only by design, quality & craftsmanship, but most importantly it's superior features. Some of the features are: Designer IMPACT DOUBLE GLASS FRONT DOOR, IMPACT WINDOWS throughout, IMPACT SLIDERS out to the oversized lanai, high ceilings, tray ceilings in Living Room and Master BR, tall baseboards, 8 foot doors throughout (incl. closet doors), tile throughout as well as on large Lanai incl. extended patio with built-in fire pit, 42" wood cabinetry in kitchen with crown molding, stainless steel appliances, quarz kitchen counters as well as in bathrooms, Luxury shower in Master Suite and beautiful tiled-in Bathroom in Hallway. Large back yard is fenced and features Mango, Avocado and Banana. The extended patio features a built-in fire pit and there is plenty of room for a pool. Garage Epoxy floor paint and built-in shelving. NOT IN A FLOOD ZONE. This is the perfect house to start a family or settle down in, an all around sound investment. Move-in ready!
